author: legospongepotter
title: Tree Tree
review: Not much to say. If you want to make a forest or something, you get ten good trees. I don't know what to say, except that it's cool to have a bunch of trees. For me, this is good as a Lego harry Potter Forbidden forest. I'll need a bunch more trees though to make it realistic. Worth it, but I doubt it'd be easy to even get it on eBay, most just get the trees alone, just one.
